Installing Flask Apps Tryton
============================

Prerequisites
-------------

 * Flask (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Flask)
 * Flask-Babel (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Flask-Babel)
 * Flask-Cache (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Flask-Cache)
 * Docutils (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/docutils)
 * PkgInfo (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pkginfo)
 * Setuptools (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools)

Configuration
-------------

config.ini

* APP NAME

config.cfg

* Debug
* Template
* Language
* Cache type

PKG-INFO
--------

Create a ln in your packages to get information module:

src/account$ ln -s trytond_account.egg-info/PKG-INFO PKG-INFO
